- futures - systemmatic, non-lineariry, network creating, mutual learning

Characteristics of the PFS:
- Publics and problems revealed as ``in the making'' p132
- Materialising potential futures as people experience them p132
- Zooming in and out p133
- Translating between different kinds of data and expertise p133
- Opening up participation p133},
