  comment          = {Draws on literature about policy entrepreneurs (originated by Kingdon 1984 [not according to vonMalmborg2024strategies], who described them as ``willingness to invest their resources -- time, energy, reputation, and sometimes money -- in the hope of a future return'') to discuss the attributes, skills and strategies of the PE

