3. training, mentoring, etc on engagement, conflict resolution, negotiation, systems thinking, teamwork
4. building partnerships e.g. between university and local community
5. create communities of practice about engagement and scalable solutions
6. funding is requred for these changes to be effective

Q\&A hosted by Rapley follows asking about:
